{"id":255118,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-长沙上访维权者刘华等17人被绑架，报警遭/","date":"2012-10-06T05:45:58Z","modified":"2012-10-06T05:45:58Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙上访维权者刘华等17人被绑架，报警遭推诿（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道） 10月2日 ，长沙上访维权者刘华等17人在北京旅游，被北京公安以查身份证为由带离北京 东方 君悦大酒店，随后交给黑保安，17人</span><span>被强拖上京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B09705</span><span>的大巴</span><span>，</span><span>遣送回长沙，期间多人被殴打，17人名单：李香，吴莎，李仲瑜，黄美珍，眭建平，段静玲，肖利红，黄振湘，穆明德，唐国玉，罗林，曾才温，江灿，骆凤球，刘桂华，丁文茵，刘华。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日</span><span>中午一行人到达长沙后，众人就遭遇绑架报警。黎托派出所警察到达现场后，既不立案，又不做笔录，也没有去抓非法拘禁</span><span>17人</span><span>的黑保安。而是坐在车里，说需要等领导答复。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>17人</span><span>报案过去了八个多小时后，长沙雨花区公安分局值班局长周仲林到达现场，说还要协调。报案过去了11个小时，市政府联席办的李处长又到现场，他说这个案件需要湖南省政法委出面协调，要求省公安厅与北京公安联合调查，当</span><span>17人</span><span>要求立案后，他说已经超出了他的业务范围。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当晚众人就睡在大街上，看住京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B09705</span><span>大巴。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点，雨花区公安分局政委章晓波组织几十名警察，强行将绑架17人的大巴车京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">B09705</span><span>开走，期间有警察拿出车钥匙打开车门。章晓波说打人事件是在北京发生的，要</span><span>17人</span><span>去北京立案。后来章晓波让大家先到黎托派出所做笔录，给“不立案决定通知书”，众人到了黎托派出所后，警方却出尔反尔不给做笔录了，章晓波也不见踪影。大家赶到雨花区公安分局，大门紧闭，门卫拒绝开门。</span><span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-d-DNiIAHctU/UG-RYcfWOnI/AAAAAAAAQmQ/xjOzQOyBaow/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-d-DNiIAHctU/UG-RYcfWOnI/AAAAAAAAQmQ/xjOzQOyBaow/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZGiQn3icB60/UG-RaLsEhRI/AAAAAAAAQmY/bZuX8XAjOkc/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZGiQn3icB60/UG-RaLsEhRI/AAAAAAAAQmY/bZuX8XAjOkc/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hsbSDNGHv9M/UG-RbRgmqQI/AAAAAAAAQmg/kvml_P-Yg3M/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hsbSDNGHv9M/UG-RbRgmqQI/AAAAAAAAQmg/kvml_P-Yg3M/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JgnS79CH39g/UG-RctV2GWI/AAAAAAAAQmk/anbRiW_828Q/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-JgnS79CH39g/UG-RctV2GWI/AAAAAAAAQmk/anbRiW_828Q/s320/4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关详情参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/10/17.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/10/17.html</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4096909525062990729?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}